rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0001
rows.name: How remarkable...

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0002
rows.name:
That view down below is the
world where we live, isn't it?

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0003
rows.name: So it would appear.

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0004
rows.name:
I had no idea it was possible for
humans to reach these kind of heights.

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0005
rows.name:
And this World Tree's been around
since forever, too.

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0006
rows.name:
I'm not sure I can keep up with
what we're finding out here.

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0007
rows.name: Hey, Prince! Look!

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0008
rows.name: Over down there!

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0009
rows.name:
What is it?
You see something?

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0010
rows.name:
Look, right over there! It's Genbu!
That's gotta be Genbu!

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0011
rows.name: Seriously?!

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0012
rows.name:
Wow, you're right...
That does look like Luxuria!

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0013
rows.name:
What are you talking about?
Of course we can't see Luxuria
from all the way up here.

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0014
rows.name:
We totally can, though!
Come over and take a look!

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0015
rows.name: How shall I respond?

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0016
rows.name: I'm sure it's just a cloud or something.

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0017
rows.name: Frankly, I'm not interested.

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0101
rows.name: I don't see any sign of Luxuria anywhere.

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0102
rows.name: Not over there, over here!

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0103
rows.name: Look, right there!

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0104
rows.name: It's so small, it's difficult to judge.

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0105
rows.name: Are you sure you're not imagining it?

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0106
rows.name:
No imagining going on here!
That's Genbu, no doubt about it!

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0107
rows.name: Hmmm... Is it, though?

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0108
rows.name: Kagutsuchi...

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0109
rows.name: What is it, Meleph-sama?

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0110
rows.name:
Well, it's just... I think I may have
spotted Superbia down there.
Do you think that's really it?

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0111
rows.name: What?

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0112
rows.name: Oh hey, you found your place too?

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0113
rows.name: Where do you mean?

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0114
rows.name:
Over there - next to that
strangely-shaped cloud...

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0115
rows.name: Ah, I see the one you mean.

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0116
rows.name:
Doesn't that distinctive shape
look just like Superbia?

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0117
rows.name:
I do believe you're right... Those wide
plains look just the right shape.

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0118
rows.name:
And those shapes flying around it
must be Divine Beast battleships!

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0119
rows.name: I thought as much!

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0120
rows.name:
Incredible how one can feel the
majesty of Superbia from all
the way up here...

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0121
rows.name: Quite right, Meleph-sama!

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0122
rows.name: Hold on, you two. Take a closer look.

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0123
rows.name:
I'm pretty sure that's the Liberalitan
islands. Superbia doesn't have
all that greenery, does it?

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0124
rows.name: Ahh...

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0125
rows.name: Urk...

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0201
rows.name: Aww, c'mon. You're no fun.

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0202
rows.name:
We've come all the way to a crazy
place like this, the least you can do
is enjoy yourself a bit!

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0203
rows.name:
I'm in the wrong here?
Might I remind you, we did not
come here to have fun.

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0204
rows.name:
Everyone needs to let their hair down
once in a while, Kagutsuchi.

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0205
rows.name: Meleph-sama?

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0206
rows.name:
Myself, I have already spotted
the Liberalitan Archipelago.

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0207
rows.name: What?! Those tiny little islands?!

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0208
rows.name:
Well, whaddaya know!
Meleph's really getting into this!

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0209
rows.name:
C'mon, Prince, we can't let
her beat us!

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0210
rows.name:
No chance of that.
Take a look over there.

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0211
rows.name: Huh? I can't see anything...

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0212
rows.name:
Look real close. There's a tiny dot
right there, see? I'm pretty sure that's
Goldmund, the Avaritia HQ!

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0213
rows.name: Goldmund?! Are you certain?!

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0214
rows.name:
Where is this dot?
I'm not seeing anything.

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0215
rows.name:
Yes, that must be Goldmund!
I'm sure of it!

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0216
rows.name: You can see it, Meleph-sama?!

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0217
rows.name:
Kagutsuchi! We must find something new
ourselves, else I fear we have lost!

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0218
rows.name: When did this become a competition?

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0219
rows.name: If that is Goldmund...

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0220
rows.name: Would that be the Maelstrom next to it?

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0221
rows.name: Um... Well... I suppose it could be?

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0222
rows.name: Oh! Look down there, Kagutsuchi!

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0223
rows.name:
The Nopon sailors on board the
Maelstrom are waving to us!

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0224
rows.name: Whaaa?!

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0225
rows.name:
Uh, Meleph, I think you might be
pushing it a bit with that one.

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0226
rows.name:
I tell you no lie, I saw it
with my own eyes!

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0227
rows.name: Seriously?

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0228
rows.name: Ah... Meleph-sama...

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0229
rows.name:
I think you may just be seeing
Tora's reflection in the window.

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0230
rows.name:
No, you're wrong. I'm certain it was the
crew of the Maelstrom!

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0232
rows.name: Well, that was a bunch of fun.

rows.label: kizunatalk039_msg0233
rows.name:
Yeah. If I learned one thing today,
it's that Meleph HATES to lose.
